sentence: weekday flights from san francisco to denver
sq2:

 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v0.flight_days||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4
